Data Sources
------------------------------------------------------------------------

The CWICR cost database aggregated and published with this software was
compiled by DataDrivenConstruction from public, licensed, and originally
collected sources. Classification codes (e.g., DIN 276 cost-group numbers,
CSI MasterFormat division numbers, NRM element codes) are used as factual
references; no standard's copyrighted descriptive text has been copied
into the database without permission.

